Package: gnuradio
Architecture: any
Depends: ${python:Depends}, python-wxgtk2.8, python-cheetah, adduser, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: python-scipy, python-matplotlib, uhd-images, python-tk
Description: GNU Radio Software Radio Toolkit
 One big package that will need to be split.

Package: gnuradio-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNU Software Defined Radio toolkit documentation
 Documentation for the GNU Radio software defined radio system
 in html and xml form.

Package: gnuradio-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNU Software Defined Radio toolkit development
 Header files for the GNU Radio software defined radio system.

Package: libgnuradio
Section: libs
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libgnuradio-atsc-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-audio-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-comedi-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-core-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-digital-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-noaa-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-pager-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-qtgui-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-trellis-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-uhd-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-video-sdl-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgnuradio-vocoder-3.5.1-0.0.0, libgruel-3.5.1-0.0.0, libvolk0.0.0
Description: Dummy package for gnuradio libraries
 Fourteen libraries are built with gnuradio.
 This is a virtual package selecting all of them.

